: 6077
Name: The Night
Translation - Muhammad Tahir-ul-Qadri: Rather (he spends) seeking the pleasure of his Lord, Most High.
Translation - Arthur J: only seeking the Face of his Lord the Most High;
Tafaseer - Tafsir al-Jalalayn: but he did this only seeking the pleasure of his Lord the Most High that is to say only seeking to secure God’s reward;
Surah : Ayat: 92:20

